00:03:54.000 --> 00:04:13.000
When I was in middle school, eSports didn’t even exist. But I really enjoyed playing games. And then I always thought about the possibility of an actual paying career in gaming for the future.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:37.000
And then eight years later, when I was 21 years old, in 1997, eSports started developing in Korea. And then that’s when I thought about how I wanted to possibly pursue a special career in the world of eSports.

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:17.000
