00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:44.000
We actually do have a specialized player like that. And that player is Oz. Oz is a very strategic player. He is especially gifted on two player maps. 

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:57.000
If we notify him that we’re going to need his special talents on a two player map, he comes up with some really excellent ideas. So I try to utilize Oz quite frequently.

